definitions.definition: A colourless , inflammable liquid hydrocarbon , methyl benzene , CH 3 .C 6 H 5 , used as a solvent , in high-octane fuels and in the production of many chemical compounds .

main_definition: ( organic chemistry ) A colourless , inflammable liquid hydrocarbon , methyl benzene , CH 3 .C 6 H 5 , used as a solvent , in high-octane fuels and in the production of many chemical compounds .
